title: Davey Jones: The Monocle Men (from DHP 34-36) (2014|Dgtl|Empire)
description:
This is "Davey Jones: The Monocle Men", serialized in "Dark Horse Presents" issues 34 thru 36.

I have to admit that I'm not quite sure why, but the subject matter of piracy is taking a definite upswing in popularity at the moment, with two concurrent major TV series and this being far from the first pirate comic I've seen this year. That said, this one is more of a mash-up with a whole lotta weirdness for its own sake... and better read than described, so I'll leave it at that. :)

By Dennis Culver, co-creator and artist of the (equally weird) "Edison Rex".
